### Create product
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sku": "TICKET-001",
  "name": "Concert Ticket",
  "priceCents": 2500
}

### Add stock
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products/{{productId}}/inventory/stock
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 500
}

### Checkout
POST http://localhost:8080/api/checkout
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: demo-key-001

{
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "quantity": 1
}
